 out under and Tables.Pub. L. 92–20385 Stat. 688section 1601 of Title 43Dec. 18, 1971Section ___3(b), referred to in par. (19), probably means subsec. (b) of , which is classified to .section 100003 of Pub. L. 117–58section 9502 of this title","Short Title, , , provided that:Pub. L. 117–58, div. K, § 100001135 Stat. 1445Nov. 15, 2021“This division [enacting this chapter and amending , Government Organization and Employees] may be cited as the ‘Minority Business Development Act of 2021’.”section 5314 of Title 5"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Agency","label":"1 Agency","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9501/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9501","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9501%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “Agency” means the Minority Business Development Agency of the Department of Commerce.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Community-based organization","label":"2 Community-based organization","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9501/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9501","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9501%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “community-based organization” has the meaning given the term in .section 7801 of title 20","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Eligible entity","label":"3 Eligible entity","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9501/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9501","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs9501%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s9501/3/A","parent